Name: ploomcake.xhtmlstrict_theme
Version: 0.1
Summary: This theme adds a xhtml strict templates to ploomcake.theme
Home-page: https://github.com/ploomcake/ploomcake.xhtmlstrict_theme
Author: Maurizio Lupo
Author-email: maurizio.lupo@redomino.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This product is an xhtml strict template layer (with some patches) of ploomcake.theme
        We focused on front end facing views.
        
        views tested:
        
        standard plone view and portlets (without authoring)
        tabs and slides views and portlets
        quickupload portlet
        action portlet
        contentwellportlet
        search
        sharing
        token role
        flowsearch
        
        
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.1 (2012-10-03)
        ----------------
        
        - Initial release
        
